snippet.title: Shark Attack  (Full Game)
snippet.description:
Shark Attack Deep Sea Adventure
Shark Attack is a new-generation of 2D arcade game. Explore the underwater adventure and help Kenny, a brave young scuba diver, restore all the broken pieces in different parts of the world.
